      <title>各国央行行长罕见发表言论，支持增加黄金储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/central-bankers-make-rare-comments-in-favor-of-bigger-gold-stash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[各国央行购买黄金是今年金价创纪录上涨的主要推动力。但央行官员很少提前发出信号，表明何时才是购买黄金的首要考虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/central-bankers-make-rare-comments-in-favor-of-bigger-gold-stash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:26:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>威利斯称新西兰经济将对降息作出反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/new-zealand-economy-will-respond-to-rate-cuts-willis-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在即将迎来执政首年之际，新西兰政府大谈经济前景，称利率下降和财政纪律将在明年重振需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/new-zealand-economy-will-respond-to-rate-cuts-willis-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港特首将在讲话中重点关注经济和酒税削减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/hong-kong-s-leader-to-focus-on-economy-liquor-tax-cut-in-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港特首将在本周的年度讲话中把促进经济作为首要任务，并借此提出包括可能削减酒税和可能采取措施加强香港金融中心地位在内的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/hong-kong-s-leader-to-focus-on-economy-liquor-tax-cut-in-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲美元贷款连续第三年创纪录下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/asia-dollar-loans-head-for-a-record-third-straight-yearly-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于剩余几个月预计缺乏大额交易，亚太地区（日本除外）美元贷款量预计将连续第三年下降，与早先的增长预测相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/asia-dollar-loans-head-for-a-record-third-straight-yearly-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市有望追随美国涨势；油价下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市有望追随华尔街的强劲表现，创下历史新高。随着对以色列袭击伊朗能源设施的担忧缓解，油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:26:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《财新》报道，中国或将筹集 8460 亿美元刺激经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-may-sell-846-billion-special-bonds-caixin-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国媒体《财新》报道，中国可能在未来三年发行 6 万亿元人民币（8460 亿美元）超长期特别国债，以提振低迷的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/china-may-sell-846-billion-special-bonds-caixin-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称以色列不会针对伊朗原油，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称以色列可能不会瞄准伊朗的原油基础设施，缓解了人们对中东紧张局势的担忧，随后油价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国摩天大楼空置引发开发商价格战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/emptying-chinese-skyscrapers-trigger-price-war-among-developers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国各大城市中，越来越多光彩夺目的摩天大楼挤满了半数以上的租户，这促使更多房东降低租金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/emptying-chinese-skyscrapers-trigger-price-war-among-developers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
